name: SkyRush (Willow & Stork Studios)
description:
You play as Marisa flying her way through danger trying to avoid all kinds of enemies.

You gain points by surviving and dodging obstacles and collecting Power-Ups in this fun and addicting game!


Run into any bugs or glitches?

Please contact us at info@willowandstork.com

*extra info*

SkyRush is a fan-game inspired by the amazing Touhou project, Touhou and all of its content/characters are owned by/and belong to ZUN/Shanghai Alice. We are in no way related to ZUN/Shanghai Alice. For more info about Touhou visit the official website: http://www16.big.or.jp/~zun/top.html http://kourindou.exblog.jp/
